InCR Instantiate a new IT System Administrative Plan
UpCR Update details relating to IT System Administrative Plan
CoCR Control the processing of IT System Administrative Plan
EcCR Accept, verify, etc. aspects of IT System Administrative Plan processing
CaCR Capture IT System Administrative Plan activity or event related information
RqCR Request manual intervention or a decision with respect to IT System Administrative Plan
GrCR Obtain permission to act in relation to IT System Administrative Plan
ReCR Retrieve details about any aspect of IT System Administrative Plan
